Things I care about and/or have done a lot of:
- Taking on early SWE challenges (setting up infra, dbs, codebase, etc)
- Evaluating early employee offers (equity, evaluating, etc)
- Improving company culture (socials, onboarding, interview process, etc)
user.intro: I'm a bay area native from the San Jose/Cupertino area who spent 4 years studying CS at UIUC and quickly realized I needed to get out of the snow and back to the west coast. Today I live in San Francisco in the Dogpatch neighborhood. I'm an avid 49ers fan and love to meet people IRL (thank god this pandemic is over) over brunch, hikes, or general hangouts. I'm building in the Supply Chain space with Wiley (also Contrary) out of our Soma office.
user.lookingFor: is to figure out how to build and scale a business :)
